  "title": "Analyst – Investment Advisory",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Our Client:</strong></p><p>Our client is a leading global investment consultancy firm known for delivering high-quality advisory services to an international and diversified client portfolio. As the firm continues to grow, we are seeking talented Analysts to join the Investment Advisory team and contribute to impactful financial and strategic projects.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>🔹 Drive the execution of consulting engagements for financial institutions and corporate clients exploring new investment opportunities.</p><p>🔹 Conduct both primary and secondary research under the direction of a project lead.</p><p>🔹 Contribute creative ideas to research methodologies and demonstrate strong problem-solving capabilities.</p><p>🔹 Deliver high levels of efficiency, accountability, and accuracy across all assigned tasks.</p><p>🔹 Collaborate closely with project teams and learn from experienced colleagues across assignments.</p><p>🔹 Consolidate research insights and prepare draft deliverables with guidance from a consulting manager.</p><p>🔹 Participate in client meetings and calls to present research findings.</p><p>🔹 Support the development and preparation of consulting proposals.</p><p><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><p>✔ Bachelor’s or Master’s degree from a top-tier university (any discipline).</p><p>✔ Up to 2 years of relevant work experience.</p><p>✔ Strong passion for business, finance, and investment research.</p><p>✔ High intellectual curiosity and excellent critical-thinking capabilities.</p><p>✔ Solid business acumen, data-driven mindset, and strong analytical skills.<br /></p><p>📩 <strong>Interested candidates, please submit your application for a confidential chat.</strong><br /></p><p>EA License Name & License Number: SMTP Consult Pte. Ltd. (23C1754)</p><p>EA Personnel Name & Registration Number: Keith Wong (R24125987)</p>",
